The paper proposes a multi-layer network for learning and inference tasks, specifically for image processing. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, given the focus on building deep networks using Bayesian factor graphs, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.CV and cs.AI.
